      "writtenOn": "2021-01-05T17:27:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I was just making them public based on DSL needs, yes.\n\nGiven that most of the IR invocations are made by functions (rather than a class), just marking them public felt cleaner to me than having to list a bunch of individual friend function signatures. I\u0027m not opposed to changing it, but that was my reasoning.",
