      "writtenOn": "2021-01-05T18:02:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Right now we have \n\n  namespace SkSL {\n  namespace dsl {\n  // bunch of free functions\n  }  \n  }\n\nWhat if we had\n\n  namespace SkSL {\n  namespace dsl {\n  class DSLCore {\n      // bunch of static functions\n  };\n  using DSLCore::For;\n  using DSLCore::Switch;\n  using DSLCore::While; // etc\n  }\n  }\n\n\nThen we could `friend class DSLCore`?\nThere might be better solutions too; this is just one thought I had.",
